{
  "sn11.17:0.1": "Saṃyutta Nikāya 11 ",
  "sn11.17:0.2": "2. Dutiyavagga ",
  "sn11.17:0.3": "17. Buddhavandanāsutta ",
  "sn11.17:1.1": "Sāvatthiyaṃ jetavane. ",
  "sn11.17:1.2": "Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā divāvihāragato hoti paṭisallīno. ",
  "sn11.17:1.3": "Atha kho sakko ca devānamindo brahmā ca sahampati yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā paccekaṃ dvārabāhaṃ nissāya aṭṭhaṃsu. ",
  "sn11.17:1.4": "Atha kho sakko devānamindo bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: ",
  "sn11.17:2.1": "“Uṭṭhehi vīra vijitasaṅgāma, ",
  "sn11.17:2.2": "Pannabhāra anaṇa vicara loke; ",
  "sn11.17:2.3": "Cittañca te suvimuttaṃ, ",
  "sn11.17:2.4": "Cando yathā pannarasāya rattin”ti. ",
  "sn11.17:3.1": "“Na kho, devānaminda, tathāgatā evaṃ vanditabbā. ",
  "sn11.17:3.2": "Evañca kho, devānaminda, tathāgatā vanditabbā: ",
  "sn11.17:4.1": "‘Uṭṭhehi vīra vijitasaṅgāma, ",
  "sn11.17:4.2": "Satthavāha anaṇa vicara loke; ",
  "sn11.17:4.3": "Desassu bhagavā dhammaṃ, ",
  "sn11.17:4.4": "Aññātāro bhavissantī’”ti. "
}